BRIEFINGC2M6_1 = "\cCFantastic job on your last mission, \cPWill\cC, but we have no time to lose. Intel's analysis on the files you brought back from the \cRStahlhimmel\cC facility tell us the \cRThor's Hammer\cC research facilities are only a part of something much bigger - the \cRHades Project\cC.";
BRIEFINGC2M6_2 = "\cCWe only have bits and pieces of information about the \cRHades Project\cC, but if our theories are correct, the \cRHades Project\cC is some kind of \cRWunderwaffe\cC that is powerful enough to destroy all of \cBEurope\cC and end the war in one fell swoop -- instant victory for \cRHitler\cC.";
BRIEFINGC2M6_3 = "\cCNow, we don't know what the \cRHades Project\cC is; for all we know, it could be some kind of super U-boat or long range nuclear missile. But, we do know that both \cRSeeteufel\cC and \cRGiftmacher\cC are leading this project, and that they are meeting in \cBTrondheim\cC in \cBNorway\cC.";
BRIEFINGC2M6_4 = "\cCThis is where you come in. \cPWill\cC, you and \cQDouglas\cC will drive to the train station in \cBBergen\cC, and catch one of the reinforcement trains to \cBTrondheim\cC. From there, you are to use any means necessary to eliminate \cRGiftmacher\cC and \cRSeeteufel\cC, and shut down the \cRHades Project\cC.";
BRIEFINGC2M6_5 = "\cCThis mission could get long, \cPWill\cC, so stay in touch with \cQDouglas\cC and watch his back, and he'll watch yours. Best of luck to both you and \cQDouglas\cC; you will need it! Oh, before you go, \cPWill\cC, \cQJuliette\cC wanted to see you in her office. Dismissed!";
BRIEFINGC2M6_6 = "\cCThis sounds like a hard one, \cPWill\cC. Two birds with one stone, once again, but this time for real, and we're definitely not gonna let \cRGiftmacher\cC escape!";
BRIEFINGC2M6_7 = "\cCI will watch your back, my friend, as long as you watch mine, but nothing in this world can break the chains between us, eh? Now, let's move out and kill those sick Nazis!";

BRIEFINGC2M6B_1 = "\cCLOL, this is C2M6_B. Better luck next time... Unless you REALLY want to play this particular mission.";
BRIEFINGC2M6B_2 = "\cCNo dialogue before C2M6_B";
